data.description: This custom home sits on 3.72 acres in Walnut Creek, outside the city limits! The INTERIOR features a custom iron front door & an oversized back glass-sliding door, an OPEN FLOOR PLAN with 10-12 ft. ceilings, upgraded lighting & plumbing fixtures, gorgeous tile & vinyl flooring, ceiling fans, granite counters, walk-in closets, 2 tankless water heaters, & 2 HVAC units.  The KITCHEN features stainless steel appliances, a double oven, a gas range, a microwave drawer, custom cabinets, a farmhouse sink, & a beautiful center island. Bonus rooms include a STUDY with barn doors & a MEDIA ROOM with a bar! The MASTER SUITE INCLUDES A SITTING AREA & an oversized walk-in closet. The MASTER BATHROOM features a double vanity, a free-standing tub, & a walk-in shower with body sprayers, a hand wand,  & rain head. The EXTERIOR is great for entertaining with an outdoor Summer kitchen with sink, & fridge, an oversized porch with ceiling fans, surround sound, wood burning fireplace, & a sprinkler system. SELLER WILL PAY $12,000 TOWARDS CLOSING COST OR RATE BUY DOWN! BUILDER WILL PROVIDE SURVEY AND TITLE POLICY. BUYER STILL HAS OPTION TO PICK FLOORS IN ALL BEDROOMS.
